Judul: Deformations on the Twisted Heisenberg-Virasoro Algebra
Abstrak: With the cohomology results on the Virasoro algebra, the authors determine the second cohomology group on the twisted Heisenberg-Virasoro algebra, which gives all deformations on the twisted Heisenberg-Virasoro algebra.
Kata Kunci: Cohomology, Deformation, Virasoro algebra, Heisenberg algebra 2000 MR Subject Classi?cation 17B56, 17B68
